Author: hce692
Text: WHAAT! You mean I don’t have to write in a paper calendar book like a 70 year old psycho?! Bless you.

Author: Imamarshmellowww
Text: I use that app too, and it’s super helpful to see the graph that shows how often you’re relapsing over time. Also I like how motivational quotes and cute pictures pop up after logging.
